alUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22DeepIP%20has%20developed%20an%20AI%20assistant%20for%20drafting%20patents.%20Check%20out%20the%20pitch%20deck%20it%20used%20to%20raise%20%2415%20million.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222026%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cofounders%20of%20DeepIP%2C%20Fran%C3%A7ois-Xavier%20Leduc%20(CEO)%20and%20Edouard%20d'Archimbaud%20(CTO).%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e2bd5263d72727e1982b2d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDeepIP's%20cofounders%2C%20Edouard%20d'Archimbaud%20and%20Fran%C3%A7ois-Xavier%20Leduc.%3Cp%3EDeepIP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDeepIP%20has%20secured%20a%20%2415%20million%20Series%20A%20investment%20to%20modernize%20patent%20drafting%20with%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20startup's%20AI%20assistant%20summarizes%20large%20documents%20and%20helps%20attorneys%20draft%20patents%20faster.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECheck%20out%20the%2017-slide%20pitch%20deck%20used%20to%20secure%20the%20fresh%20funding.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20startup%20that%20has%20developed%20an%20AI%20assistant%20to%20help%20draft%20patents%20has%20just%20secured%20a%20%2415%20million%20Series%20A.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParis%20and%20New%20York-based%20DeepIP%20wants%20to%20modernize%20and%20simplify%20the%20process%20of%20filing%20patents%20%E2%80%94%20which%20can%20be%20notoriously%20lengthy%20in%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20for%20attorneys%20and%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPatents%20are%20the%20foundation%20of%20capitalism.%20Without%20patents%2C%20companies%20can't%20invest%20in%20research%20and%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20Fran%C3%A7ois-Xavier%20Leduc%2C%20the%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20DeepIP%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20says%20its%20platform%20can%20summarize%20large%20documents%2C%20simplify%20complex%20jargon%2C%20highlight%20novel%20aspects%20of%20the%20innovation%2C%20and%20spot%20any%20omissions%20in%20the%20patent%20draft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20helps%20users%20draft%20patent%20claims%20by%20suggesting%20alternative%20ways%20to%20structure%20their%20arguments.%20Leduc%20said%20DeepIP's%20AI%20assistant%20is%20designed%20to%20work%20alongside%20a%20human%20patent%20practitioner%20rather%20than%20replace%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20start%20developing%20an%20invention%2C%20you%20have%20to%20understand%20the%20entire%20space%20to%20make%20sure%20it's%20novel.%20Before%2C%20all%20this%20work%20was%20extremely%20limited%20due%20to%20human%20capabilities%2C%26quot%3B%20Leduc%20said.%20%26quot%3BAI%20allows%20us%20to%20fully%20understand%20at%20scale%2C%20the%20entire%20space%2C%20helping%20companies%20to%20identify%20how%20to%20position%20their%20inventions%2C%20and%20make%20sure%20it's%20novel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20also%20says%20it%20regularly%20tests%20and%20validates%20its%20AI%20models%20to%20ensure%20there%20are%20as%20few%20hallucinations%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestor%20appetite%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F15-legal-tech-startups-ai-raised-most-vc-funding-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elegal%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20high%2C%20with%20upstarts%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2025%2F02%2F12%2Flegal-ai-startup-harvey-300-million-series-d-funding-3-billion-valuation-sequoia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20raking%20in%20%24300%20million%20in%20funding%20last%20month%20at%20a%20%243%20billion%20valuation.%20DeepIP%20says%20its%20platform%20is%20gaining%20traction%20among%20corporations%2C%20as%20well%20as%20law%20firms%20such%20as%20Schwegman%20Lundberg%20Woessner%2C%20and%20has%20already%20helped%20draft%208%2C500%20patent%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeepIP's%20Series%20A%20was%20led%20by%20