%20because%20I%20did%20a%20Thumps%20Up%20commercial%20with%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI've%20worked%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20South%20actors.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20was%20the%20first%20Hindi%20film%20actor%20from%20my%20generation%20to%20start%20working%20with%20South%20directors.%20I've%20worked%20with%20four-five%20South%20directors%20at%20one%20point%20of%20time.%C2%A0%20Even%20the%20heroines%20share%20this%20sense%20of%20brotherhood%20with%20me%3B%20it's%20really%20nice%20%3Cem%3E(laughs)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EHow%20are%20the%20South%20directors%20different%20from%20Hindi%20filmmakers%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESalman%20Khan%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ETechnically%2C%20they're%20very%20advanced%20and%20emotionally%20they're%20very%20evolved.%20They%20don't%20pick%20up%20ideas%20and%20stories%20from%20elsewhere.%20They%20conceive%20their%20own%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20that%2C%20it's%20not%20like%20all%20the%20films%20that%20they%20make%20in%20the%20South%20are%20good.%20In%20Bollywood%2C%20you%20only%20remember%20those%20films%20that%20work%20well%20at%20the%20box%20office.%20%3Cem%3EWahaan%20bhi%20hafte%20mein%202-3%20picture%20picture%20banti%20hai%20but%20woh%20kuch%20khaas%20karti%20nahi%20hai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(2-3%20movies%20are%20released%20every%20week%20in%20the%20South%20too%2C%20but%20they%20all%20don't%20do%20too%20well).%C2%A0The%20mantra%20is%20the%20same%20everywhere.%20If%20you%20make%20good%20films%2C%20they'll%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESikandar%20%3C%2Fem%3Emarks%20Salman%20Khan%20and%20Rashmika%20Mandanna's%20first%20collaboration.%20Apart%20from%20Salman%20Khan%20and%20Rashmika%2C%20the%20project%20also%20features%20Kajal%20Aggarwal%2C%20Sathyaraj%20and%20Sharman%20Joshi%20in%20important%20roles.%20%3Cem%3ESikandar%3C%2Fem%3E%20hits%20the%20theatres%20this%20Sunday%2C%20March%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743058140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.nd