0the%20IPL%202025%20opener.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fkolkata-knight-riders-told-to-move-out-of-kolkata-amid-pitch-row-theyre-paying-for-8021312%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20Adore%20Women%26quot%3B%3A%20French%20Actor%20Depardieu%20At%20Sexual%20Assault%20Trial%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFrench%20actor%20Gerard%20Depardieu%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20he%20loved%20women%20and%20was%20not%20a%20%26quot%3Bgroper%26quot%3B%20as%20he%20made%20a%20final%20plea%20at%20his%20sexual%20assault%20trial%20in%20Paris%2C%20after%20his%20friend%20and%20fellow%20actor%20Fanny%20Ardant%20vouched%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20adore%20women%20and%20femininity%2C%20I%20feel%20very%20feminine%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20sparking%20laughter%20in%20the%20Paris%20courtroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDepardieu%2C%20who%20has%20acted%20in%20more%20than%20200%20films%20and%20television%20series%2C%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20improper%20behaviour%20by%20around%2020%20women%20but%20this%20is%20the%20first%20case%20to%20come%20to%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2076-year-old%20is%20the%20highest-profile%20figure%20to%20face%20accusations%20in%20French%20cinema's%20response%20to%20the%20%23MeToo%20movement%2C%20which%20he%20told%20the%20court%20on%20Tuesday%20would%20become%20%26quot%3Ba%20reign%20of%20terror%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20relates%20to%20charges%20of%20sexual%20assault%20during%20the%20filming%20in%202021%20of%20%26quot%3BLes%20Volets%20Verts%26quot%3B%20(%26quot%3BThe%20Green%20Shutters%26quot%3B)%20by%20director%20Jean%20Becker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnouk%20Grinberg%2C%20a%20prominent%20actor%20who%20appeared%20in%20the%20film%2C%20has%20backed%20the%20two%20plaintiffs%20--%20a%20set%20dresser%2C%2054%2C%20identified%20only%20as%20Amelie%2C%20and%20a%2034-year-old%20assistant%20director%20who%20both%20allege%20sexual%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Ardant%2C%20describing%20Depardieu%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Blifelong%20friend%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20she%20had%20never%20seen%20him%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bshocking%26quot%3B%20gesture%20towards%20a%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20you%20can%20say%20no%20to%20Gerard%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2076-year-old%20added%2C%20pausing%20on%20her%20way%20out%20of%20the%20courtroom%20to%20kiss%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20afternoon%2C%20a%20director%20of%20photography%2C%20chief%20sound%20engineer%2C%20and%20head%20stagehand%20on%20%26quot%3BLes%20Volets%20Verts%26quot%3B%20said%20they%20had%20not%20seen%20Depardieu%20behave%20inappropriately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E'Grunting'%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20three%20witnesses%20for%20the%20prosecution%20told%20stories%20similar%20to%20those%20of%20the%20two%20plaintiffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrying%2C%20a%20journalist%20called%20Marie%20said%20Depardieu%20had%20in%202007%20kneaded%20her%20back%20%26quot%3Bwhile%20grunting%26quot%3B%2C%20descending%20towards%20her%20knickers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarah%20B.%20said%20she%20was%2020%20when%20she%20appeared%20in%20the%20Netflix%20series%20%26quot%3BMarseille%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20actor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20put%20his%20hand%20in%20my%20knickers%20against%20my%20skin.%20I%20pushed%20him%20away%2C%20he%20did%20it%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20costume%20designer%20called%20Lucile%20said%20she%20gave%20up%20cinema%20%26quot%3Bdisgusted%26quot%3B%20after%20Depardieu%20assaulted%20her%20in%202014.%20She%20filed%20a%20legal%20complaint%20last%20year%2C%20but%20the%20statute%20of%20limitations%20had%20expired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20shoved%20me%20behind%20curtains%2C%20put%20his%20hand%20on%20my%20knickers%2C%20my%20tights%2C%20my%20sex%2C%20my%20breasts.%20He%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20do%20all%20sorts%20of%20things%20with%20me%2C%20that%20others%20had%20said%20yes%2C%20and%20that%20others%20would%20say%20yes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2034-year-old%20plaintiff%2C%20who%20was%20third%20assistant%20director%20during%20filming%2C%20said%20Wednesday%20that%20Depardieu%20groped%20her%20as%20she%20accompanied%20him%20from%20his%20room%20to%20set%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20and%20then%20on%20two%20more%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20night%20his%20team%20wasn't%20there.%20We%20left%20his%20room%2C%20it%20was%20nighttime.%20And%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20road%2C%20he%20put%20his%20hand%20on%20my%20bum%2C%20he%20placed%20it%20there%20calmly%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20he%20then%20twice%20touched%20her%20breasts%20and%20buttocks%20on%20two%20occasions%2C%20and%20she%20told%20him%20%26quot%3Bno%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Foul-mouthed'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20said%20he%20was%20never%20alone%20on%20set%2C%20always%20accompanied%20by%20a%20dresser%2C%20makeup%20artist%20or%20bodyguard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20perhaps%20brushed%20past%20her%20in%20the%20corridor%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20touch%20her.%20I%20didn't%20commit%20sexual%20assault%2C%20I%20think%20sexual%20assault%20is%20more%20serious%20than%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20lawyer%20asked%3A%20%26quot%3BMore%20serious%20than%20what%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDepardieu%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BMore%20serious%20than%20a%20hand%20on%20a%20bum.%20That%20is%2C%20I%20didn't%20put%20a%20hand%20on%20a%20bum.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20vulgar%2C%20rude%2C%20foul-mouthed%2C%20I'll%20accept%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20but%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20touch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDepardieu%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20he%20was%20not%20in%20the%20habit%20of%20%26quot%3Bgroping%26quot%3B%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20had%20grabbed%20Amelie%2C%20the%20set%20dresser%2C%20by%20the%20h