0significant%20achievement%20in%20population%20control%20and%20contribution%20to%20the%20country's%20GDP%2C%20he%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20language%20issue%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20questioned%20why%20the%20DMK%20was%20against%20Hindi%20and%20said%20it%20was%20essential%20to%20learn%20every%20language.%20%26quot%3BThe%20country%20should%20not%20be%20divided%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20language%20or%20region.%20We%20are%20grateful%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20ji%20for%20organising%20the%20third%20generation%20of%20the%20Kashi-Tamil%20Sangamam%20in%20Varanasi.%20Tamil%20is%20one%20of%20the%20oldest%20languages%20in%20India%2C%20and%20its%20history%20is%20as%20ancient%20as%20Sanskrit.%20Every%20Indian%20has%20respect%20and%20reverence%20for%20Tamil%20because%20many%20elements%20of%20Indian%20heritage%20are%20still%20alive%20in%20the%20language.%20So%2C%20why%20should%20we%20hate%20Hindi%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20DMK's%20stand%20as%20%26quot%3Bnarrow%20politics%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20these%20people%20feel%20their%20vote%20bank%20is%20at%20risk%2C%20they%20try%20to%20create%20divisions%20based%20on%20region%20and%20language.%20The%20people%20of%20this%20country%20should%20always%20be%20alert%20to%20such%20divisive%20politics%20and%20stand%20firm%20for%20the%20unity%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Mr%20Stalin%20said%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20stand%20on%20the%20two-language%20and%20delimitation%20was%20%26quot%3Bechoing%20nationwide%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20BJP%20is%20%26quot%3Bclearly%20rattled%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20now%20Hon'ble%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20wants%20to%20lecture%20us%20on%20hate%3F%20Spare%20us.%20This%20isn't%20irony%20-%20it's%20political%20black%20comedy%20at%20its%20darkest.%20We%20don't%20oppose%20any%20language%3B%20we%20oppose%20imposition%20and%20chauvinism.%20This%20isn't%20riot-for-votes%20politics.%20This%20is%20a%20battle%20for%20dignity%20and%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743048060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F9pa1k478_mk-stalin-yogi-split_625x300_27_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmk-stalin-yogi-adityanath-black-comedy-at-its-darkest-mk-stalins-reply-to-yogi-adityanaths-barbs-8020755%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20sharp%20reply%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath's%20criticism%20over%20the%20three-language%20row%2C%20his%20Tamil%20Nadu%20counterpart%20MK%20Stalin%20has%20said%20the%20firebrand%20leader's%20remarks%20are%20not%20irony%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20black%20comedy%20at%20its%20darkest%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmk-stalin-yogi-adityanath-black-comedy-at-its-darkest-mk-stalins-reply-to-yogi-adityanaths-barbs-8020755%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'If%20you%20do%20not%20leave%2C%20will%20hunt%20you%20down'%3A%20US'%20Kristi%20Noem%20threatens%20to%20send%20more%20immigrants%20to%20El%20Salvador%20prison%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743047882000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119572194%2Cimgsize-29226.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fif-you-do-not-leave-will-hunt-you-down-us-kristi-noem-threatens-to-send-more-immigrants-to-el-salvador-prison%2Farticleshow%2F119571421.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F119571421.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EUS%20homeland%20security%20Secretary%20Kristi%20Noem%20visited%20a%20high-security%20El%20Salvador%20prison%20housing%20Venezuelan%20detainees%20deported%20under%20accusati