ia%20post%20on%20Wednesday.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Sullivan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E23andMe%20cofounder%20Linda%20Avey%20discussed%20the%20company%20in%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAvey%20said%20the%20biotech%20company%20%26quot%3Blost%20its%20way%26quot%3B%20without%20product%20development%20and%20%26quot%3Bproper%20governance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E23andMe%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy%2C%20and%20CEO%20Anne%20Wojcicki%20resigned%20this%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftimeline-the-rise-and-fall-of-23andme-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E23andMe%3C%2Fa%3E%20cofounder%20Linda%20Avey%20is%20mourning%20what%20the%20biotech%20company%20could%20have%20become.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAvey%20reflected%20on%2023andMe%20%E2%80%94%20and%20criticized%20former%20CEO%20Anne%20Wojcicki%20%E2%80%94%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fpulse%2Fthoughts-23andme-linda-avey-kbqof%2F%3FtrackingId%3DD2cw%252ForoE%252BaQRR88rU5SfQ%253D%253D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bit%20was%20time%20to%20express%20my%20views%20on%20the%20company%2C%20after%20witnessing%20the%20downfall%20of%20an%20idea%20and%20brand%20that%20could%20have%20become%20the%20world's%20leading%20digital%20health%20platform.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F23andme-bankruptcy-chapter-11-anne-wojcicki-quits-dna-testing-google-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E23andMe%20filed%20for%20Chapter%2011%20bankruptcy%20protection%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20announced%20Wojcicki's%20resignation.%20Avey%20worked%20alongside%20Wojcicki%20and%20Paul%20Cusenza%20to%20launch%20the%20biotech%20company%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20nearly%20twenty%20years%20ago.%20The%20company%20makes%20direct-to-consumer%20DNA%20test%20kits%20and%20explores%20genetic%20research.%20Avey%20served%20as%20co-president%20from%202006%20to%202009%20and%20remained%20a%20company%20board%20member%20until%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20post%2C%20Avey%20said%20the%20idea%20for%2023andMe%20sparked%20after%20working%20in%20life%20science%20research%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lightbulb%20went%20on%20%E2%80%94%20if%20I%20was%20interested%20in%20accessing%20my%20own%20data%2C%20wouldn't%20others%20feel%20the%20same%20way%3F%20Getting%20deeply%20personalized%20information%20about%20what%20makes%20us%20'us'%20seemed%20undeniable.%20It%20didn't%20take%20long%20for%20the%20concept%20to%20unfold%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAvey%20said%20she%20pursued%20this%20goal%20under%2023andMe%20until%202009%2C%20when%20her%20time%20at%20the%20company%20was%20%26quot%3Bcut%20short.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20time%20at%20the%20company%20was%20cut%20short%20in%202009%2C%20when%20my%20co-founder%20Anne%20convinced%20the%20board%20that%20she%20should%20run%20the%20company.%20And%20I%20must%20be%20honest%2C%20I%20was%20frustrated%20with%20the%20direction%20the%20company%20took%20after%20that%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20Avey%20said.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20my%20departure%2C%20she%20architected%20a%20majority%20vote%20for%20herself%20that%20eliminated%20board%20governance%2C%20even%20as%20the%20board%20expanded%20over%20the%20following%20funding%20rounds.%20For%20better%20or%20worse%2C%20the%20buck%20stopped%20with%20her.%20It%20came%20as%20no%20surprise%20when%20the%20board%20resigned%20last%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAvey%20said%20that%2023andMe%20%26quot%3Bwas%20in%20a%20unique%20position%26quot%3B%20initially%2C%20and%20it's%20%26quot%3Bpainful%20to%20think%20what%20could%20have%20been.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20company%20has%20amassed%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20genetic%20data%20collections%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20to%20Anne's%20credit%2C%20created%20a%20terrific%20consumer%20brand.%20We%20can%20only%20imagine%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20dataset%20that%20could%20have%20been%20built%2C%20combining%20blood%20work%2C%20deeper%20gene%20sequencing%2C%20wearable%20data%2C%20and%20providing%20actionable%20insights%2C%26quot%3B%20Avey%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20the%20market%20is%20fragmented%20with%20data%20siloed%20in%20many%20different%20companies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAvey%20said%2023andMe%20%26quot%3Blost%20its%20way%26quot%3B%20without%20%26quot%3Bconsumer-focused%20product%20development%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bproper%20governance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%2014%2B%20million%20people%20who%20bought%20into%20the%20concept%20deserve%20to%20see%20their%20data%20moved%20to%20a%20secure%20platform%20with%20new%20leadership%20and%20vision%2C%26quot%3B%20Avey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAvey%20rounded%20out%20her%20statement%20by%20emphasizing%20the%20importance%20of%20a%20balanced%20C-Suite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20many%20cautionary%20tales%20buried%20in%20the%2023andMe%20story.%20Striking%20a%20balance%20between%20the%20desire%20for%20founder%20control%20and%20board%20oversight%20is%20essential%3B%20otherwise%2C%20why%20have%20a%20board%20at%20all%3F'%20Avey%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20familiar%20trope%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20that%20wealth%20translates%20into%20unquestionable%20business%20savvy.%20But%20no%20matter%20how%20great%20an%20idea%2C%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20dynamics%20of%20the%20founding%20team%20and%20their%20ability%20to%20listen%20to%20feedback%20is%20key.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAvey%2C%20Wojcicki%2C%20and%20representatives%20for%2023andMe%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222eb4d498-77d3-44ac-adb9-7acb0097f51c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E23andMe%20struggled%20before%20filing%20for%20bankruptcy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E23andMe%20has%20weathered%20several%20storms%20since%202023.%3C%2