0of%20the%20dough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20might%20not%20make%20the%20best%20sourdough%20loaf%2C%20this%20is%20the%20ideal%20dough%20for%20focaccia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBefore%20committing%20to%20focaccia%2C%20try%20to%20shape%20your%20loaf.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20relatively%20flat%20loaf%20of%20sourdough%20bread.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e4371e63d72727e1984da7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20flat%20loaf%20of%20sourdough%20bread.%3Cp%3EAli%20Majdfar%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20were%20set%20on%20making%20a%20sourdough%20loaf%2C%20don't%20give%20up%20just%20because%20your%20dough%20looks%20slightly%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20advice%20is%20to%20go%20ahead%20and%20try%20to%20shape%20the%20dough%20into%20a%20loaf.%20I%20do%20this%20for%20a%20few%20reasons.%20First%2C%20it's%20practice%20at%20shaping.%20Second%2C%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20best%20signs%20of%20whether%20you%20must%20resort%20to%20focaccia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20shape%20your%20dough%20and%20it%20falls%20flat%20and%20refuses%20to%20hold%20a%20round%2C%20firm%20shape%2C%20then%20you%20know%20you%20should%20probably%20pop%20it%20in%20a%20pan%20and%20make%20focaccia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20focaccia%20recipe%20is%20simple.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20active%20sourdough%20starter.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e437db69253ccddf9a5b79%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20reporter's%20active%20sourdough%20starter.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20use%20the%20same%20recipe%20for%20baking%20a%20sourdough%20loaf%20and%20focaccia.%20%3Cspan%3EIt%20comes%20from%20this%20TikToker%20and%20self-described%20sourdough%20enthusiast%20named%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40casacalifano%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EJackie%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20calls%20for%20500%20grams%20of%20bread%20flour%2C%20375%20grams%20of%20water%2C%2011%20grams%20of%20salt%2C%20and%20100%20grams%20of%20active%20sourdough%20starter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20setting%20out%20to%20make%20focaccia%2C%20you%20can%20skip%20all%20the%20confusing%20stretch%20and%20folds%20and%20just%20mix%20the%20ingredients%20and%20let%20it%20sit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20long%20you%20let%20it%20sit%20depends%20on%20your%20home's%20temperature%2C%20but%20typically%2C%20you%20need%20to%20let%20it%20rest%20for%20more%20than%20eight%20hours.%20You%20can%20also%20toss%20the%20dough%20in%20the%20fridge%20overnight%20to%20bake%20the%20next%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20it's%20rested%20and%20doubled%2C%20toss%20it%20in%20a%20pan%20with%20olive%20oil%20and%20dimple%20the%20dough.%20Then%2C%20you%20wait%20another%20three%20or%20four%20hours%20before%20baking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20focaccia%20is%20simple%3A%20don't%20stress%20about%20timing.%20If%20you%20wait%20six%20hours%20instead%20of%20four%2C%20your%20dough%20will%20likely%20be%20fine.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou're%20ultimately%20looking%20for%20a%20rested%20dough%20that%20has%20plenty%20of%20bubbles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIf%20you're%20a%20sourdough%20beginner%2C%20focaccia%20is%20ideal.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20loaf%20of%20sourdough%20sits%20on%20a%20food%20scale.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e4393169253ccddf9a5bb6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20scale%20is%20helpful%20to%20measure%20our%20ingredients%20for%20a%20sourdough%20recipe.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wish%20I%20had%20known%20how%20easy%20it%20was%20to%20make%20focaccia%20when%20I%20started%20my%20sourdough%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20waited%20months%20before%20using%20my%20starter%20because%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20Dutch%20oven%20or%20the%20right%20tools%20to%20make%20a%20sourdough%20loaf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaking%20sourdough%20focaccia%20doesn't%20require%20any%20special%20equipment.%20A%20scale%20is%20handy%20but%20not%20necessary%20since%20you%20can%20find%20recipes%20using%20cups%20online.%20Plus%2C%20you%20can%20bake%20focaccia%20in%20a%20brownie%20pan%2C%20sheet%20tray%2C%20or%20whatever%20you%20have%20handy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20a%20bread%20that's%20harder%20to%20mess%20up%2C%20which%20means%20you'll%20have%20delicious%20bread%20and%20more%20confidence%20to%20continue%20baking%20sourdough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFocaccia%20is%20my%20go-to%20if%20I'm%20experimenting%20with%20toppings%20and%20flavors.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20savory%20and%20sweet%20sourdough%20focaccia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e4388769253ccddf9a5b8d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20savory%20and%20sweet%20sourdough%20focaccia.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20reasons%20I%20love%20focaccia%20is%20how%20easy%20it%20is%20to%20add%20toppings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20methods%20for%20incorporating%20flavors%20and%20inclusions%20into%20a%20sourdough%20loaf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20if%20I%20made%20a%20jalape%C3%B1o%20cheddar%20loaf%2C%20some%20bakers%20would%20add%20the%20peppers%20and%20cheese%20during%20the%20stretch%20and%20fold%20process%2C%20while%20others%20would%20add%20them%20during%20the%20shaping%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20led%20to%20issues.%20Sometimes%2C%20the%20toppings%20are%20concentrated%20in%20one%20part%20of%20the%20loaf%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20get%20a