%20years%20researching%20the%20optimal%20temperatures%20for%20the%20freeze-drying%20technique.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20they%20focused%20solely%20on%20delivering%20within%20their%20local%20area%20and%20were%20not%20yet%20catering%20to%20a%20wider%20audience.%20In%20April%202024%2C%20after%20perfecting%20the%20consistency%20and%20taste%20and%20gaining%20valuable%20insights%20from%20numerous%20rounds%20of%20feedback%2C%20they%20launched%20a%20website%20to%20begin%20accepting%20orders%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20invested%20time%20and%20effort%20into%20sourcing%20the%20right%20freeze-drying%20technology%20to%20meet%20their%20specific%20needs.%20While%20it%20is%20not%20a%20new%20concept%2C%20particularly%20in%20industries%20like%20pharmaceuticals%20(where%20powdered%20antibiotics%20are%20prepared%20using%20freeze-drying%20technology)%20and%20space%20food%20(where%20astronauts%20rely%20on%20it%20for%20long-term%20meals)%2C%20it%20had%20never%20been%20customised%20for%20the%20ready-to-eat%20food%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20researching%20in%20the%20Indian%20market%20for%20our%20freeze-drying%20machine%20after%20exploring%20various%20options%20in%20China.%20The%20machine%20we%20have%20is%20custom-made%20according%20to%20our%20requirements%2C%20specifically%20for%20our%20meals.%E2%80%9D%20The%20couple%20realised%20that%20the%20existing%20models%20for%20freeze-drying%20food%20were%20not%20tailored%20for%20the%20kind%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333562%2Fassam-daily-wager-diganta-das-launches-paratha-startup-inspiring-entrepreneur-in-food-business%2F%5C%22%20target%3