ut%20nothing%20could%20compete%20with%20Sunday%20lunches%2C%20where%20the%20table%20brimmed%20with%20authentic%20South%20Indian%20dishes.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20feast!%20Sometimes%2C%20friends%20and%20relatives%20would%20drop%20by%2C%20and%20other%20times%2C%20we%20would%20have%20unexpected%20guests%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chef%20Sriram%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20choosing%20a%20career%2C%20Chef%20Sriram%20ventured%20into%20law%2C%20but%20later%2C%20at%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20behest%2C%20he%20explored%20culinary%20pursuits.%20He%20joined%20the%20Institute%20of%20Hotel%20Management%2C%20Catering%20Technology%20and%20Applied%20Nutrition%20in%20India%20in%201984%20and%20followed%20this%20up%20with%20a%20post-graduate%20degree%20in%20food%20production%20skills%20and%20management%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20which%20paved%20his%20way%20into%20the%20Taj%20Hotel%20in%20Mumbai.%20Here%2C%20the%20young%20chef%20was%20exposed%20to%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20best%20chefs%2C%20talent%2C%20and%20the%20finest%20ingredients%E2%80%9D.%20His%20subsequent%20travels%20around%20the%20world%20made%20him%20cognisant%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357260%2Fbest-street-food-mumbai-chef-sanjyot-keer-your-food-lab-ashok-vada-pav-mamledar-misal-elco-bandra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epotential%20of%20Indian%20flavours%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20made%20him%20want%20to%20formalise%20his%20love%20affair%20with%20food.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20first%20project%20was%20the%20%E2%80%98Karavalli%E2%80%99%20restaurant%2C%20created%20in%201990%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20which%20went%20on%20to%20be%20featured%20among%20the%20